channel.title: TextDrawingArea problem!
channel.description:
Yeah, I was adding a Mod tool interface for staff members, but I got this problem...
[code] Java\RSInterface.java:264: error: cannot find symbol StaffTab(TextDrawingArea); ^ symbol: variable TextDrawingArea location: class RSInterface Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Didn't find any way to fix this..
